column5: probably a long shot,but has anyone been to beech lake in Minden? im heading up there for 2 days starting tuesday and will probably get in a little bit of fishing time. ive tried to do a little bit of scouting on the lake via google and havent come up with much at all. read,trout,muskie and LM bass. if anyones been there and would like to offer any advice im all ears.....and eyes.
